StructureRI: The table is in the form of an array (i.e. the rows) of arrays (containing the values in the columns). The first row gives the names of the columns. Note that JSON arrays maintain the order of the elements see https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8259#page-7
SemanticRI: The table has columns: (1) Identifier as a pair IdentifierType and Identifier, (2)Type of package - should be AIP, (3) Is the AIP declared to be complete - yes/no, (4) Package description as English text
